EdVisitFact

The emergency department visit fact contains information about emergency department visits. Each row represents an emergency department visit.

    PAT_ENC_HSP.PAT_ID

    If ADMIT_CONF_STAT_C <> 3 AND ADT_PATIENT_STAT_C IS NOT NULL AND ADT_PATIENT_STAT_C <> 6 AND ( INP_ADM_DATE IS NOT NULL OR ADT_PAT_CLASS_C is in {Observation Patient Classes} ) THEN PAT_ENC_HSP.PAT_ENC_CSN_ID If there exists another PAT_ENC_CSN_ID where PAT_ID is the same and INP_ADM_DATE is within 60 minutes of the original discharge then PAT_ENC_CSN_ID. Otherwise, empty.
